<info xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="https://apps.nextcloud.com/schema/apps/info.xsd">
	<id>arbeitszeitcheck</id>
	<name>ArbeitszeitCheck / TimeGuard</name>
	<summary>Legally compliant time tracking system for German labor law (ArbZG) and GDPR</summary>
	<description>
		ArbeitszeitCheck is a comprehensive, legally compliant time tracking system specifically designed for German organizations.
		It fully implements German labor law (Arbeitszeitgesetz - ArbZG) requirements including mandatory break times,
		maximum working hours, rest periods, and Sunday/holiday work tracking.

		Key features:
		- German labor law compliance (ArbZG, ECJ C-55/18)
		- GDPR compliant data processing and employee rights
		- Real-time compliance monitoring and violation alerts
		- Employee self-service portal with dashboard
		- Manager approval workflows
		- Vacation and absence management
		- Project time tracking integration (optional)
		- Comprehensive reporting and exports
		- WCAG 2.1 AAA accessibility compliance
		- Mobile-responsive design
		- Audit logging and data retention management

		This system ensures organizations meet all legal requirements while providing employees with
		full transparency and control over their working time data.
	</description>

